                <p class="title">♡ welcome to match your sock! ♡</p>

                <div class="radios">
                    <p>
                        "match your sock" is a website where owners of no-longer-matching socks from all over the world can come together to 
                        pair them with each other.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        no matter the length, colour, and age of your sock, they all deserve a second chance at life, and 
                        to not be lonely anymore.
                    </p>
                </div>
