                    <p>
                        please be respectful of all sock owners, and be sure to write in the point of view of your sock. they deserve a voice, too!
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        please report any inappropriate behaviour to our admin team, and let us know once you have paired up your sock. we will add a 
                        "found" tag to your post!
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
